            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Well the goal of this issue is to merely improve maintainability (for you, mostly). If you deem it to be less maintainable than the current situation I'll drop the suggestion :)\n\nIt seems to me something like this is much more maintainable:\n\n```yml\nsponsors:\n  - image: images/sponsors/cool-sponsor.png\n    name: CoolSponsor\n    page: home # or tier: X or something else\n    start_date: 2026-05-05\n    end_date: 2026-08-05\n  - image: ...\n```",
